Class LeaderCard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.leadercard.LeaderCard
All Implemented Interfaces:
VictoryPointsElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConvertLeaderCard, DiscountLeaderCard, ProduceLeaderCard, StoreLeaderCard
public abstract class LeaderCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements VictoryPointsElement
Card of which each player has 2 of. Has special abilities which are automatically applied to all actions of the owner when active. Can be discarded when inactive and will grant a 1 step movement on the faith track to its owner.
